siness/autos-transportation/bmw-group-annual-sales-fall-weak-demand-china-germany-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国新的人工智能芯片规则将如何运作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</link><description>该规则规范了最复杂的人工智能应用所需的美国人工智能芯片和技术的流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国收紧对全球人工智能芯片流动的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</link><description>美国政府表示，将进一步限制人工智能芯片和技术出口，瓜分全球，将先进计算能力保留在美国及其盟友手中，同时寻找更多方式阻止中国进入。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达表示新规定将削弱美国在人工智能领域的领导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nvidia-says-new-rule-will-weaken-us-leadership-ai-2025-01-13/</link><description>英伟达周一批评拜登政府为加强华盛顿对全球人工智能芯片流动的控制而采取的新举措，称该规定将危及美国目前在人工智能领域的领导地位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nvidia-says-new-rule-will-weaken-us-leadership-ai-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>英国和毛里求斯表示查戈斯群岛谈判取得良好进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mauritius-say-good-progress-made-chagos-islands-talks-2025-01-13/</link><description>英国和毛里求斯周一表示，谈判在敲定查戈斯群岛主权协议（包括美英军事基地）方面取得了良好进展，伦敦希望在唐纳德·特朗普就职前签署该协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mauritius-say-good-progress-made-chagos-islands-talks-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国制裁收紧对俄罗斯石油的控制，中国和印度寻求新的供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-india-refiners-scour-world-oil-supplies-us-sanctions-curb-russian-supply-2025-01-13/</link><description>许多贸易商周一表示，由于美国对俄罗斯生产商和油轮的新制裁将成为迄今为止限制向莫斯科最大客户发货的最有效措施，中国和印度炼油商正在寻求替代原油供应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-india-refiners-scour-world-oil-supplies-us-sanctions-curb-russian-supply-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>协会数据显示2025年中国汽车出口增速将放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-vehicle-export-growth-slow-2025-association-data-shows-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国汽车工业协会 (CAAM) 周一公布的数据显示，今年中国汽车出口量预计将增长 5.8%，达到 620 万辆，较 2024 年 19.3% 的增幅有所降温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:58:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-vehicle-export-growth-slow-2025-association-data-shows-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>花旗集团任命 Jeff Wu 为中国市场销售主管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-names-jeff-wu-china-markets-sales-head-2025-01-13/</link><description>路透社周一看到的一份内部备忘录显示，花旗集团已任命 Jeff Wu 为中国市场销售主管，立即生效，旨在统一其在中国所有市场产品的销售工作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:13:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-names-jeff-wu-china-markets-sales-head-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷2024年中国销量下降28%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-2024-china-sales-fall-by-28-2025-01-13/</link><description>德国跑车制造商保时捷公司周一报告称，由于全球最大汽车市场的持续疲软对德国汽车制造商造成打击，2024 年中国销量下降 28%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-2024-china-sales-fall-by-28-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>陆军参谋长表示，印度不会在冬季减少中国边境驻军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-looking-reduce-troops-along-northern-frontier-winter-army-chief-says-2025-01-13/</link><description>印度陆军参谋长周一表示，印度不打算在冬季减少北部边境的军队数量，并补充说，印度将根据与中国的谈判结果审查夏季部署。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-looking-reduce-troops-along-northern-frontier-winter-army-chief-says-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾对北京在南海的“升级行动”提出抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-protest-over-beijings-escalatory-actions-south-china-sea-2025-01-13/</link><description>菲律宾周一呼吁北京停止在南海浅滩采取“升级行动”，并表示已就中国海岸警卫队、民兵和海军出现在其专属经济区提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-protest-over-beijings-escalatory-actions-south-china-sea-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国调查发现中国不公平地主导造船业，为处罚铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-probe-finds-china-unfairly-dominates-shipbuilding-paving-way-penalties-2025-01-13/</link><description>三名熟悉为期数月贸易调查结果的消息人士告诉路透社，美国总统乔·拜登政府得出的结论是，中国利用不公平的政策和做法来主导全球海事、物流和造船行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-probe-finds-china-unfairly-dominates-shipbuilding-paving-way-penalties-2025-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>